reviewText:
This game is simply AWESOME now with the latest patch! You should definitively get it ! Why?

- Great turn based tactical battles with very good AI ( hard to find these days );

- Mixture of multiple factions , choices that alter the course of the game and game modes that boosts replayability ( you WILL want to finish the game multiple times );

- Beautiful and optimized graphics / and art lets you enjoy on lighter specs Rigs

- UNLIKE 99% of the games on Steam , Devs listen to community , keep active , and work very hard to please customers;

I have over 1000 games and I dont remember the last time I came across something so nice.


When this game came out , it had great potential but some major issues that preventing it from being an awesome game. I was one of the many people who got disapointed , and I am leaving my original review below so you can compare my thoughts about the game before and after.




***Original OUTDATED review***  Patches mentioned below were all BEFORE Redux

Unfortunately this game is a prime example of a sad waste of potential. If could have been great if it werent for the combat system that ruins it - the fact that a patch that completely alters the combat system came out just shows how critical it is. And even with the patch I cant say it is good enough. Not when you played the older X-Com and Fallout series.
Too bad , I wish I could recommend this game :-(
